ः","m":"best horse"},{"d":"युक्तम्","m":"yoked"},{"d":"आदित्यसङ्काशम्","m":"effulgent as the Sun"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"आस्थाय","m":"taking seat"},{"d":"वालिपुत्रम्","m":"Vali's son"},{"d":"अभ्ययात्","m":"marched."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"स त्रिभिर्देवदर्पघ्नेर्नेरृतीन्द्रेरभिद्रुतः ।वृक्षमुत्पाटयामासमहाविटपमङ्गदः","trans":"Angada observed that all the three chiefs of Rakshasas, who were capable of crushing the pride of gods marching towards him and uprooted a huge tree.","words":[{"d":"देवदर्पघ्नेः","m":"capable of crushing the pride of gods"},{"d":"त्रिभिः","m":"all the three"},{"d":"नैरृतेन्द्रः","m":"chiefs of Rakshasas अभिद्रुतः marching towards"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"अङ्गदः","m":"Angada"},{"d":"महाविटपम्","m":"huge"},{"d":"वृक्षम्","m":"tree"},{"d":"उत्पाटयामास","m":"uprooted."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"देवान्तकायतंवीरच्शिक्षेपसहसाङ्गदः ।महावृक्षंमहाशाखंशक्रोदीप्तमिवाशनिम्","trans":"Just as Indra took a flaming thunderbolt, Angada, the hero took hold of huge branches of trees and hurled at Devanthaka with force.","words":[{"d":"वीरः","m":"hero"},{"d":"अङ्गदः","m":"Angada"},{"d":"महाशाखम्","m":"huge branches"},{"d":"तम्","m":"those"},{"d":"महावृक्षम्","m":"huge tree"},{"d":"शक्रः","m":"branches"},{"d":"दीप्तम्","m":"flaming"},{"d":"अशनम् इव","m":"flaming thunderbolt"},{"d":"सहसा","m":"with force"},{"d":"देवान्तकाय","m":"Devanthaka"},{"d":"चिक्षेप","m":"hurled."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"त्रिशिरास्तंप्रचिच्छेदशरैराशीविषोपमैः ।स वृक्षंकृत्तमालोक्यउत्पपाततदाङ्गदः","trans":"Trisira split the trees with the arrows which were like venomous serpents. Observing Angada's action he flew up.","words":[{"d":"त्रिशिराः","m":"Trisira"},{"d":"आशीविषोपमैः","m":"venomous serpents"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"तम्","m":"them"},{"d":"प्रचिच्छेद","m":"split"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"कृत्तम्","m":"action"},{"d":"वृक्षम्","m":"trees"},{"d":"आलोक्य","m":"observing"},{"d":"सःअङ्गदः","m":"that Angada"},{"d":"उत्पपात","m":"flew up."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"स ववर्षततोवृक्षान् शैलाश्चकपिकुञ्जरः