ra's action), was happy on the battlefield, and went with his club to assault Hanuman.","words":[{"d":"बली","m":"mighty"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"देवान्तकः","m":"Devanthaka"},{"d":"आहवे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"हर्षात्","m":"happy"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"मारुतात्मजम्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"आलोक्य","m":"observing"},{"d":"परिघेण","m":"with his club"},{"d":"अभिदुद्राव","m":"assaulted."}]},{"v":24,"dev":"तमापतन्तमुत्प्लुत्यहनुमान्मारुतात्मजः ।आजघानतदामूर्ध्निवज्रकल्पेनमुष्टिना","trans":"Then the son of wind god, Hanuman observing Devanthaka coming towards him, got up and hit him on the forehead with his thunderbolt like fist.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"मारुतात्मजः","m":"son of wind god"},{"d":"हनुमान्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"उत्पत्य","m":"got up"},{"d":"वज्रकल्पेन","m":"which was like a thunderbolt"},{"d":"मुष्टिना","m":"with fist"},{"d":"मूर्ध्नि","m":"forehead"},{"d":"आजघान","m":"hit."}]},{"v":25,"dev":"शिरसिप्रहरवनीरस्तदावायुसुतोबली ।नादेनाकम्पयच्चैवराक्षसान् स महाकपिः","trans":"When the heroic and strong son of the wind god hit on the head of Devanthaka, the Rakshasas trembled by the sound of the great monkey 's blow.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"वीरः","m":"heroic"},{"d":"बली","m":"strong"},{"d":"वायुसुतः","m":"son of wind god"},{"d":"शिरसि","m":"on head"},{"d":"प्रहरत्","m":"blow"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"महाकपिः","m":"great monkey"},{"d":"नादेन","m":"sound"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"अकम्पयच्चैव","m":"trembled."}]},{"v":26,"dev":"मुष्टिनिष्पिष्टविभिन्नमूर्धानिर्वान्तदन्ताक्षिविलम्बिजिव्वाः ।देवान्तकोराक्षसराजसूनुर्गतासुरुत्व्यांसहसापपात","trans":"Devanthaka's skull was shattered by the blow, and his teeth, eyes and tongue were forced out, the son of Rakshasa king fell dead on the ground.","words":[{"d":"मुष्टिनिष्पिष्टविभिन्नमूर्धा","m":"skull shattered by the blow"},{"d":"निर्वान्तदन्ताक्षिविलम्बिजिव्वाः","m":"teeth, eyes and tongue forced out"},{"d":"राक्षसराजसूनुः","m":"son of king of Rakshasas"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"